{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "zv9cp2jrso0",
    "category": "news",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZV9CP2JrsO0",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mom, Dad, look at my report card!",
      "zh": "媽媽，爸爸，看看我的成績單！",
      "ja": "お母さん、お父さん、私の成績表を見て！",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Wow!",
      "zh": "哇！",
      "ja": "わあ！",
      "time": "00:00:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Lily, an A-plus.",
      "zh": "莉莉，A加分。",
      "ja": "リリー、Aプラスだね。",
      "time": "00:00:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is amazing.",
      "zh": "這真是太棒了。",
      "ja": "これはすごいね。",
      "time": "00:00:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We are so proud of you, Lily.",
      "zh": "我們為你感到驕傲，莉莉。",
      "ja": "リリー、私たちはあなたをとても誇りに思っているよ。",
      "time": "00:00:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You worked very hard.",
      "zh": "你努力了很多。",
      "ja": "よく頑張ったね。",
      "time": "00:00:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Lily, this is a gift for you.",
      "zh": "莉莉，這是給你的禮物。",
      "ja": "リリー、これはあなたへのプレゼントだよ。",
      "time": "00:00:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Go ahead, open it and see what's inside.",
      "zh": "快打開看看裡面是什麼。",
      "ja": "さあ、開けて中を見てごらん。",
      "time": "00:00:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A laptop, thank you, Dad.",
      "zh": "一台筆記型電腦，謝謝你，爸爸。",
      "ja": "ノートパソコンだ、ありがとうパパ。",
      "time": "00:00:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you, Mom.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，媽媽。",
      "ja": "ありがとうママ。",
      "time": "00:00:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Wow, a laptop.",
      "zh": "哇，一台筆記型電腦。",
      "ja": "わあ、ノートパソコンだ。",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My result is next.",
      "zh": "接下來是我的成績。",
      "ja": "次は私の成績だ。",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe I will get a big gift, too.",
      "zh": "也許我也會得到一份大禮物。",
      "ja": "私も大きなプレゼントをもらえるかも。",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nora, this is a sea-grade, this is not good.",
      "zh": "諾拉，這是海洋等級，這不好。",
      "ja": "ノラ、これは海の成績だ、良くないよ。",
      "time": "00:00:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sorry, Dad.",
      "zh": "對不起，爸爸。",
      "ja": "ごめんね、パパ。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But, do I have a gift?",
      "zh": "但是，我有禮物嗎？",
      "ja": "でも、プレゼントはある？",
      "time": "00:00:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you, Dad.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，爸爸。",
      "ja": "ありがとうパパ。",
      "time": "00:00:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "An alarm clock, why?",
      "zh": "一個鬧鐘，為什麼？",
      "ja": "目覚まし時計？なぜ？",
      "time": "00:00:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nora, you waste your time.",
      "zh": "諾拉，你浪費時間。",
      "ja": "ノラ、時間を無駄にしているよ。",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You sleep too much.",
      "zh": "你睡太多了。",
      "ja": "寝すぎだよ。",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You play games too much.",
      "zh": "你玩遊戲太多了。",
      "ja": "ゲームをやりすぎだ。",
      "time": "00:01:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You need to know the value of time.",
      "zh": "你需要知道時間的價值。",
      "ja": "時間の大切さを知る必要がある。",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This clock will help you.",
      "zh": "這個鐘會幫助你。",
      "ja": "この時計が助けてくれるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nora, remember this.",
      "zh": "諾拉，記住這點。",
      "ja": "ノラ、これを覚えておいて。",
      "time": "00:01:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Gifts come from hard work.",
      "zh": "禮物來自努力。",
      "ja": "プレゼントは努力から生まれる。",
      "time": "00:01:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Gifts are not free.",
      "zh": "禮物不是免費的。",
      "ja": "プレゼントは無料じゃない。",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I hate this clock, I hate this gift.",
      "zh": "我討厭這個鐘，我討厭這個禮物。",
      "ja": "この時計が嫌い、このプレゼントが嫌い。",
      "time": "00:01:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Lily is the favorite.",
      "zh": "莉莉是最受寵愛的。",
      "ja": "リリーが一番のお気に入りだ。",
      "time": "00:01:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Mom and Dad love her.",
      "zh": "媽媽和爸爸愛她。",
      "ja": "お母さんとお父さんは彼女を愛している。",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They do not love me.",
      "zh": "他們不愛我。",
      "ja": "彼らは私を愛していない。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Lily is my enemy.",
      "zh": "莉莉是我的敵人。",
      "ja": "リリーは私の敵だ。",
      "time": "00:01:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe I should hide Lily's laptop.",
      "zh": "也許我應該藏起莉莉的筆記型電腦。",
      "ja": "リリーのノートパソコンを隠そうかな。",
      "time": "00:02:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maybe I should break it.",
      "zh": "也許我應該把它弄壞。",
      "ja": "壊してしまおうかな。",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It is not fair.",
      "zh": "這不公平。",
      "ja": "不公平だ。",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am not special.",
      "zh": "我不特別。",
      "ja": "私は特別じゃない。",
      "time": "00:02:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No one in this house cares about me.",
      "zh": "這個家沒有人關心我。",
      "ja": "この家では誰も私のことを気にかけていない。",
      "time": "00:02:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good morning, Nora.",
      "zh": "早安，諾拉。",
      "ja": "おはよう、ノラ。",
      "time": "00:02:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you want some juice?",
      "zh": "你想喝點果汁嗎？",
      "ja": "ジュースいる？",
      "time": "00:02:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, I do not want anything.",
      "zh": "不，我什麼都不想要。",
      "ja": "いいえ、何もいりません。",
      "time": "00:02:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you okay?",
      "zh": "你還好嗎？",
      "ja": "大丈夫？",
      "time": "00:02:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nora?",
      "zh": "諾拉？",
      "ja": "ノラ？",
      "time": "00:02:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Be quiet, Lily.",
      "zh": "安靜，莉莉。",
      "ja": "静かにして、リリー。",
      "time": "00:02:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You are just a show-off.",
      "zh": "你只是愛炫耀。",
      "ja": "あなたはただの見せびらかしだ。",
      "time": "00:02:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You think you are better than me because of your laptop.",
      "zh": "你以為因為你的筆記型電腦你比我強。",
      "ja": "ノートパソコンがあるから私より優れていると思っている。",
      "time": "00:02:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I was just trying to help.",
      "zh": "我只是想幫忙。",
      "ja": "助けようとしただけだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nora, do not speak to your sister like that.",
      "zh": "諾拉，不要那樣跟你妹妹說話。",
      "ja": "ノラ、妹にそんな言い方をしないで。",
      "time": "00:02:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nora, sit down and eat your breakfast.",
      "zh": "諾拉，坐下來吃早餐。",
      "ja": "ノラ、座って朝ごはんを食べなさい。",
      "time": "00:02:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am not hungry.",
      "zh": "我不餓。",
      "ja": "お腹すいてない。",
      "time": "00:02:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "David, maybe the alarm clock was too much.",
      "zh": "大衛，也許鬧鐘太過分了。",
      "ja": "デイビッド、目覚まし時計はちょっとやりすぎかも。",
      "time": "00:03:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nora looks really sad.",
      "zh": "諾拉看起來真的很難過。",
      "ja": "ノラは本当に悲しそうだ。",
      "time": "00:03:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I do not want to hurt her heart.",
      "zh": "我不想傷害她的心。",
      "ja": "彼女の心を傷つけたくない。",
      "time": "00:03:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I love Nora.",
      "zh": "我愛諾拉。",
      "ja": "ノラを愛している。",
      "time": "00:03:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "But she must learn because she needs to learn.",
      "zh": "但她必須學習，因為她需要學習。",
      "ja": "でも彼女は学ばなければならない、必要だから。",
      "time": "00:03:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Life is about effort.",
      "zh": "人生就是努力。",
      "ja": "人生は努力だ。",
      "time": "00:03:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "If she does not work hard now, her future will be difficult.",
      "zh": "如果她現在不努力，未來會很困難。",
      "ja": "今努力しなければ、将来は大変になる。",
      "time": "00:03:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The clock is a lesson, not a punishment.",
      "zh": "這個鐘是一堂課，不是懲罰。",
      "ja": "この時計は罰ではなく教訓だ。",
      "time": "00:03:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, it was not because they hate me.",
      "zh": "哦，不是因為他們討厭我。",
      "ja": "ああ、彼らが私を嫌っているわけじゃなかった。",
      "time": "00:03:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It was a lesson.",
      "zh": "那是一堂課。",
      "ja": "それは教訓だった。",
      "time": "00:03:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why is this so hard?",
      "zh": "為什麼這麼難？",
      "ja": "なぜこんなに難しいの？",
      "time": "00:04:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I do not get anything.",
      "zh": "我什麼都不懂。",
      "ja": "何もわからない。",
      "time": "00:04:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I cannot do this.",
      "zh": "我做不到。",
      "ja": "できない。",
      "time": "00:04:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am not smart like Lily.",
      "zh": "我不像莉莉那麼聰明。",
      "ja": "リリーみたいに賢くない。",
      "time": "00:04:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nora, can I come in?",
      "zh": "諾拉，我可以進來嗎？",
      "ja": "ノラ、入ってもいい？",
      "time": "00:04:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, go away, Lily.",
      "zh": "不，走開，莉莉。",
      "ja": "いや、行ってリリー。",
      "time": "00:04:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I do not want to talk.",
      "zh": "我不想說話。",
      "ja": "話したくない。",
      "time": "00:04:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Please, Nora, just listen to me for a minute.",
      "zh": "拜託，諾拉，聽我說一分鐘。",
      "ja": "お願い、ノラ、ちょっとだけ聞いて。",
      "time": "00:04:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Why are you here to show me how smart you are?",
      "zh": "你為什麼來這裡炫耀你多聰明？",
      "ja": "なんでここに来て自分の賢さを見せつけるの？",
      "time": "00:04:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, I came because you are my sister.",
      "zh": "不，我來是因為你是我妹妹。",
      "ja": "違うよ、君が私の妹だから来たんだ。",
      "time": "00:04:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Then why does it feel like I am always behind you?",
      "zh": "那為什麼我總覺得自己落後你？",
      "ja": "じゃあ、なぜいつも君の後ろにいる気がするの？",
      "time": "00:04:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You are not behind me, Nora.",
      "zh": "你沒有落後我，諾拉。",
      "ja": "君は私の後ろじゃないよ、ノラ。",
      "time": "00:04:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You are learning in a different way.",
      "zh": "你用不同的方式學習。",
      "ja": "違う方法で学んでいるんだ。",
      "time": "00:05:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I try so hard and still fail.",
      "zh": "我很努力但還是失敗。",
      "ja": "一生懸命やっても失敗する。",
      "time": "00:05:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That does not mean you are not smart.",
      "zh": "那不代表你不聰明。",
      "ja": "それは君が賢くないって意味じゃない。",
      "time": "00:05:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You just need help.",
      "zh": "你只是需要幫助。",
      "ja": "ただ助けが必要なだけだよ。",
      "time": "00:05:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We are a team.",
      "zh": "我們是一隊的。",
      "ja": "私たちはチームだ。",
      "time": "00:05:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We can study together every day.",
      "zh": "我們可以每天一起學習。",
      "ja": "毎日一緒に勉強できるよ。",
      "time": "00:05:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A team?",
      "zh": "一隊？",
      "ja": "チーム？",
      "time": "00:05:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:05:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "If you want, you can use my laptop.",
      "zh": "如果你願意，可以用我的筆記型電腦。",
      "ja": "もしよければ、私のノートパソコンを使っていいよ。",
      "time": "00:05:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We can study together every day.",
      "zh": "我們可以每天一起學習。",
      "ja": "毎日一緒に勉強しよう。",
      "time": "00:05:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You would really help me after how I behaved.",
      "zh": "我這樣對你，你還願意幫我。",
      "ja": "私の態度の後でも助けてくれるの？",
      "time": "00:05:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Of course.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "もちろん。",
      "time": "00:05:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You are my sister.",
      "zh": "你是我妹妹。",
      "ja": "君は私の妹だよ。",
      "time": "00:05:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You are not angry with me.",
      "zh": "你不生我的氣。",
      "ja": "私に怒っていないの？",
      "time": "00:05:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No, Nora, I love you.",
      "zh": "不，諾拉，我愛你。",
      "ja": "違うよ、ノラ、愛してる。",
      "time": "00:05:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am sorry, Lily.",
      "zh": "對不起，莉莉。",
      "ja": "ごめんね、リリー。",
      "time": "00:06:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I was wrong.",
      "zh": "我錯了。",
      "ja": "間違ってた。",
      "time": "00:06:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I said bad things.",
      "zh": "我說了壞話。",
      "ja": "悪いことを言った。",
      "time": "00:06:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It is okay.",
      "zh": "沒關係。",
      "ja": "大丈夫だよ。",
      "time": "00:06:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What matters is you are trying now.",
      "zh": "重要的是你現在正在努力。",
      "ja": "大事なのは今頑張っていることだよ。",
      "time": "00:06:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, let us start today.",
      "zh": "好，讓我們今天開始。",
      "ja": "よし、今日から始めよう。",
      "time": "00:06:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That is my sister.",
      "zh": "那是我的妹妹。",
      "ja": "それが私の妹だ。",
      "time": "00:06:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We will do this together.",
      "zh": "我們會一起做這件事。",
      "ja": "一緒にやろう。",
      "time": "00:06:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The next two weeks are very busy.",
      "zh": "接下來兩週會很忙。",
      "ja": "これからの2週間はとても忙しい。",
      "time": "00:06:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Every day, Nora and Lily study together.",
      "zh": "每天，諾拉和莉莉一起學習。",
      "ja": "毎日、ノラとリリーは一緒に勉強する。",
      "time": "00:06:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The room is quiet.",
      "zh": "房間很安靜。",
      "ja": "部屋は静かだ。",
      "time": "00:06:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, Nora.",
      "zh": "好，諾拉。",
      "ja": "よし、ノラ。",
      "time": "00:06:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let us start with something easy.",
      "zh": "讓我們從簡單的開始。",
      "ja": "簡単なことから始めよう。",
      "time": "00:06:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Are you ready?",
      "zh": "你準備好了嗎？",
      "ja": "準備はいい？",
      "time": "00:06:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I think so, but what if I get it wrong?",
      "zh": "我想是，但如果我答錯怎麼辦？",
      "ja": "たぶんね、でも間違えたらどうしよう？",
      "time": "00:06:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Then you learn.",
      "zh": "那你就學習。",
      "ja": "そうしたら学ぶんだよ。",
      "time": "00:06:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That is how it works.",
      "zh": "事情就是這樣運作的。",
      "ja": "それが仕組みだよ。",
      "time": "00:06:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, let us try.",
      "zh": "好，我們試試看。",
      "ja": "よし、やってみよう。",
      "time": "00:06:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is the answer 12?",
      "zh": "答案是12嗎？",
      "ja": "答えは12？",
      "time": "00:06:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:06:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That is correct.",
      "zh": "答對了。",
      "ja": "正解だよ。",
      "time": "00:06:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Really?",
      "zh": "真的嗎？",
      "ja": "本当？",
      "time": "00:06:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I got it right.",
      "zh": "我答對了。",
      "ja": "正解した。",
      "time": "00:06:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes, I knew I could do it.",
      "zh": "是的，我知道我能做到。",
      "ja": "うん、できると思ってたよ。",
      "time": "00:07:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is so exciting.",
      "zh": "這真令人興奮。",
      "ja": "とてもワクワクする。",
      "time": "00:07:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I want to sleep more.",
      "zh": "我想多睡一會兒。",
      "ja": "もっと寝たい。",
      "time": "00:07:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "No, I have to wake up.",
      "zh": "不，我得醒來。",
      "ja": "ダメ、起きなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:07:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Lily, I am so tired.",
      "zh": "莉莉，我好累。",
      "ja": "リリー、疲れた。",
      "time": "00:07:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can we stop now?",
      "zh": "我們現在可以停了嗎？",
      "ja": "もうやめていい？",
      "time": "00:07:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Just one more page.",
      "zh": "再一頁就好。",
      "ja": "あと1ページだけ。",
      "time": "00:07:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You are doing great.",
      "zh": "你做得很好。",
      "ja": "よくできてるよ。",
      "time": "00:07:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "One more page.",
      "zh": "再一頁。",
      "ja": "もう1ページ。",
      "time": "00:07:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:07:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Lily, I solved this by myself.",
      "zh": "莉莉，我自己解出來了。",
      "ja": "リリー、これ自分で解けたよ。",
      "time": "00:07:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That is amazing, Nora.",
      "zh": "太棒了，諾拉。",
      "ja": "すごいね、ノラ。",
      "time": "00:07:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is actually fun now.",
      "zh": "現在真的很有趣。",
      "ja": "今は本当に楽しい。",
      "time": "00:07:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I do not understand this part.",
      "zh": "我不懂這部分。",
      "ja": "この部分がわからない。",
      "time": "00:07:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It is okay.",
      "zh": "沒關係。",
      "ja": "大丈夫。",
      "time": "00:08:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let us break it into small steps.",
      "zh": "讓我們分成小步驟。",
      "ja": "小さなステップに分けよう。",
      "time": "00:08:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, step by step.",
      "zh": "好，一步一步來。",
      "ja": "うん、一歩ずつ。",
      "time": "00:08:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nora uses the clock every day.",
      "zh": "諾拉每天使用這個鐘。",
      "ja": "ノラは毎日時計を使っている。",
      "time": "00:08:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She studies, takes breaks, and studies again.",
      "zh": "她學習，休息，再學習。",
      "ja": "勉強して、休憩して、また勉強する。",
      "time": "00:08:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She is changing.",
      "zh": "她正在改變。",
      "ja": "彼女は変わっている。",
      "time": "00:08:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝你。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:08:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You really helped me.",
      "zh": "你真的幫助了我。",
      "ja": "本当に助けてくれた。",
      "time": "00:08:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nora, how was your test?",
      "zh": "諾拉，你的考試怎麼樣？",
      "ja": "ノラ、テストはどうだった？",
      "time": "00:08:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do not be scared.",
      "zh": "不要害怕。",
      "ja": "怖がらないで。",
      "time": "00:08:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Just tell us.",
      "zh": "告訴我們就好。",
      "ja": "教えて。",
      "time": "00:08:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Please, just see it.",
      "zh": "拜託，看看這個。",
      "ja": "お願い、これを見て。",
      "time": "00:08:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Sarah, look at this.",
      "zh": "莎拉，看看這個。",
      "ja": "サラ、これを見て。",
      "time": "00:08:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What happened?",
      "zh": "發生什麼事了？",
      "ja": "何があったの？",
      "time": "00:08:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "She did it.",
      "zh": "她做到了。",
      "ja": "彼女はやったよ。",
      "time": "00:08:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nora got an A.",
      "zh": "諾拉得了A。",
      "ja": "ノラはAを取った。",
      "time": "00:08:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh, Nora, we are so proud of you.",
      "zh": "哦，諾拉，我們為你感到驕傲。",
      "ja": "ああ、ノラ、私たちはとても誇りに思っているよ。",
      "time": "00:09:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I really tried this time.",
      "zh": "這次我真的很努力。",
      "ja": "今回は本当に頑張った。",
      "time": "00:09:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nora, this is for you.",
      "zh": "諾拉，這是給你的。",
      "ja": "ノラ、これは君のためだよ。",
      "time": "00:09:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You earned it.",
      "zh": "你應得的。",
      "ja": "君が勝ち取ったんだ。",
      "time": "00:09:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It is a laptop.",
      "zh": "這是一台筆記型電腦。",
      "ja": "ノートパソコンだよ。",
      "time": "00:09:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You worked hard.",
      "zh": "你努力了。",
      "ja": "よく頑張ったね。",
      "time": "00:09:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is your reward.",
      "zh": "這是你的獎勵。",
      "ja": "これは君へのご褒美だ。",
      "time": "00:09:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Nora, aren't you going to use it?",
      "zh": "諾拉，你不打算用它嗎？",
      "ja": "ノラ、使わないの？",
      "time": "00:09:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you for helping me.",
      "zh": "謝謝你幫助我。",
      "ja": "助けてくれてありがとう。",
      "time": "00:09:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "For not giving up on me.",
      "zh": "謝謝你沒有放棄我。",
      "ja": "私を諦めなかったことに感謝する。",
      "time": "00:09:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You did the hard work.",
      "zh": "是你努力的結果。",
      "ja": "君が努力したんだよ。",
      "time": "00:09:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I just helped a little.",
      "zh": "我只是稍微幫忙。",
      "ja": "私は少し手伝っただけ。",
      "time": "00:09:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now I understand.",
      "zh": "現在我明白了。",
      "ja": "今わかったよ。",
      "time": "00:09:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My tests come from effort.",
      "zh": "我的考試成績來自努力。",
      "ja": "テストの結果は努力の賜物だ。",
      "time": "00:09:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's right, Nora.",
      "zh": "沒錯，諾拉。",
      "ja": "その通りだよ、ノラ。",
      "time": "00:09:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And this was my first real gift.",
      "zh": "這是我第一份真正的禮物。",
      "ja": "そしてこれが私の初めての本当のプレゼントだった。",
      "time": "00:10:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Really?",
      "zh": "真的嗎？",
      "ja": "本当？",
      "time": "00:10:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The clock?",
      "zh": "那個鐘？",
      "ja": "あの時計？",
      "time": "00:10:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:10:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "At first, I hated it.",
      "zh": "一開始我討厭它。",
      "ja": "最初は嫌いだった。",
      "time": "00:10:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I thought it was a punishment.",
      "zh": "我以為那是懲罰。",
      "ja": "罰だと思っていた。",
      "time": "00:10:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "And now, now I know it was a lesson.",
      "zh": "現在，我知道那是一堂課。",
      "ja": "でも今は、それが教訓だったとわかる。",
      "time": "00:10:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It taught me the value of time.",
      "zh": "它教會我時間的價值。",
      "ja": "時間の大切さを教えてくれた。",
      "time": "00:10:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I am glad you understand.",
      "zh": "我很高興你明白了。",
      "ja": "理解してくれてうれしいよ。",
      "time": "00:10:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The laptop is nice, but the time I saved and the work I did that is my real success.",
      "zh": "筆記型電腦很好，但我節省的時間和我做的努力才是真正的成功。",
      "ja": "ノートパソコンはいいけど、節約した時間と努力したことが本当の成功だ。",
      "time": "00:10:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I am proud of you, Nora.",
      "zh": "我為你感到驕傲，諾拉。",
      "ja": "ノラ、誇りに思うよ。",
      "time": "00:10:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We are proud of both of you.",
      "zh": "我們為你們兩個都感到驕傲。",
      "ja": "二人とも誇りに思っているよ。",
      "time": "00:10:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Subscribe now for more loving family stories.",
      "zh": "現在訂閱，獲取更多溫馨的家庭故事。",
      "ja": "今すぐ登録して、もっと心温まる家族の物語を見よう。",
      "time": "00:10:53"
    }
  ]
}